<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />

    <title>@ViewBag.Title :: @ViewBag.BlogMeta?.Title</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.11.2/css/all.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/layout.main.css" />

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="side">
            <div class="profile">
                <img src="@ViewBag.BlogMeta?.Owner.Image" />
                <div class="profile-text">
                    <h5>허강준 <span class="account">@@0x00000FF</span></h5>
                    <p>소개글 블라블라 써보는데 그냥 제대로 된 위치에 있는건가 확인할 뿐이니 크게 의미는 두지 않습니다 이거 ㄹㅇ임</p>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-sns">
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/0x00000FF" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kangjun-heo-7002b8171/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/0x00000FF" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="side-block">
                <form action="/Search">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="전체검색" />
                    <button>S</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="side-block">
                <ul id="categories">
                    <li>전체목록 <span class="category-post-count">(3)</span></li>
                    <li>Category1</li>
                    <li>
                        Category1
                        <ul class="category-sub">
                            <li>Category 1-1</li>
                            <li>Category 1-2</li>
                            <li>Category 1-3</li>
                            <li>Category 1-4</li>
                            <li>Category 1-5</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Category1</li>
                    <li>Category1</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="side-block">

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="container">
                @RenderBody()
            </div>
            <footer class="p-3">
                Copyright &copy; @ViewBag.BlogMeta?.Owner.Name @DateTime.Now.Year, All rights reserved.
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
